title: Transfer problem
body: Can't get transfer between Eune and Euw region for past 2 hours but still can login in Eune server.

replies.body: Got same problem here, it wont transfer me to Russia but I can log in back on west

I have your account pulled up now, and that's hella weird that you've tried so many times and it still won't go through. Typically we'd ask that you try to wait a day to see if that issue clears itself up, but if you'd like to go ahead and shoot EU a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new), they should be able to manually push the transfer through for you!
